# Developer:  馃唩 馃吘 馃叡 馃叴 馃唩 馃唭 馃吘  馃叢 馃叞 馃吇 馃叞 馃叡 馃唩 馃叴 馃唫 馃叴
# City:       馃吙 馃叞 馃吇 馃叴 馃唩 馃吋 馃吘, 馃唫 馃吀 馃叢 馃吀 馃吇 馃唸
# Country:    馃吀 馃唭 馃叞 馃吇 馃唸

# Keys 						Action
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Meta + Del                      Log out
Ctrl + Alt + Del                Reboot
Meta + Ctrl + Alt + Del         Shutdown
Meta + Escape                   Restart 'XDG portals'

Meta + F1                       Toggle 'gamemode'
Meta + F                        Toggle 'fullscreen' on the 'focussed' window.
Meta + J                        Toggle 'split' mode
Meta + P                        Toggle 'pseudo' windows
Meta + T                        Toggle 'floating' for the 'focussed' window
Meta + Alt + Ctrl + T           Toggle 'floating' for 'all' windows

Meta + V                        Open  the 'clipboard'
Meta + Alt + Ctrl + V           Clear the 'clipboard'

Meta + B                        Toggle the visibility of 'Waybar'
Meta + W                        Reload 'Waybar'

Meta + ArrowUp                  Set the 'focus' on the window on the 'left'   of the current one
Meta + ArrowDown                Set the 'focus' on the window on the 'right'  of the current one
Meta + ArrowLeft                Set the 'focus' on the window on the 'top'    of the current one
Meta + ArrowRight               Set the 'focus' on the window on the 'bottom' of the current one

Meta + Alt + ArrowLeft          Resize the 'focussed' window to the 'left'   by 60 pixels
Meta + Alt + ArrowRight         Resize the 'focussed' window to the 'right'  by 60 pixels
Meta + Alt + ArrowUp            Resize the 'focussed' window to the 'top'    by 60 pixels
Meta + Alt + ArrowDown          Resize the 'focussed' window to the 'bottom' by 60 pixels

Meta + RightMouseButton         Resize the 'window' under the cursor
Meta + LeftMouseButton          Move the 'window' under the cursor

Meta + 1                        Switch to 'Desktop 1'
Meta + 2                        Switch to 'Desktop 2'
Meta + 3                        Switch to 'Desktop 3'
Meta + 4                        Switch to 'Desktop 4'
Meta + 5                        Switch to 'Desktop 5'
Meta + 6                        Switch to 'Desktop 6'
Meta + 7                        Switch to 'Desktop 7'
Meta + 8                        Switch to 'Desktop 8'
Meta + 9                        Switch to 'Desktop 9'
Meta + 0                        Switch to 'Desktop 10'

Meta + Alt + 1                  Put the 'focussed' window to 'Desktop 1'
Meta + Alt + 2                  Put the 'focussed' window to 'Desktop 2'
Meta + Alt + 3                  Put the 'focussed' window to 'Desktop 3'
Meta + Alt + 4                  Put the 'focussed' window to 'Desktop 4'
Meta + Alt + 5                  Put the 'focussed' window to 'Desktop 5'
Meta + Alt + 6                  Put the 'focussed' window to 'Desktop 6'
Meta + Alt + 7                  Put the 'focussed' window to 'Desktop 7'
Meta + Alt + 8                  Put the 'focussed' window to 'Desktop 8'
Meta + Alt + 9                  Put the 'focussed' window to 'Desktop 9'
Meta + Alt + 0                  Put the 'focussed' window to 'Desktop 10'

Meta + Q                        Close the 'focussed' window

Meta + ScrollDown               Walk through active 'desktops'
Meta + ScrollUp                 Walk through active 'desktops' (Reverse)

Meta + Alt + Ctrl + Return      Open 'Konsole'
Meta + Alt + Return             Open 'Alacritty'
Meta + Alt + A                  Open 'Amarok'
Meta + Alt + C                  Open 'Calculator'
Meta + Alt + D                  Open 'Dolphin'
Meta + Alt + F                  Open 'Firefox'
Meta + Alt + G                  Open 'Gimp'
Meta + Alt + K                  Open 'KDE Settings'
Meta + Alt + I                  Open 'Inkscape'
Meta + Alt + M                  Open 'Weather Forecast'
Meta + Alt + N                  Open 'Netflix'
Meta + Alt + P                  Open 'Color Picker HEX'
Meta + Alt + Ctrl + P           Open 'Color Picker RGB'
Meta + Alt + Q                  Open 'Qbittorrent'
Meta + Alt + S                  Open 'Sublime Text'
Meta + Alt + T                  Open 'Tor Browser'
Meta + Alt + V                  Open 'Virtualbox'

Menu                            Open 'Application launcher'
Print                           Open 'hp-print'
Scroll_lock                     Open 'hyprshot-gui'